    "This involves processing and interpreting large volumes of textual data from sources like online reviews, social media, and customer service interactions [150,151].For food quality, sentiment analysis identifies consumer perceptions related to taste, texture, and packaging, enabling businesses to improve product quality based on customer feedback."
